From Henry Spencer Subject Re Why not give billion to first year long moon residents In article Allen Sherzer writes This prize isn't big enough to warrent developing a SSTO but it is enough to do it if the vehicle Actually there are people who will tell you that it would be enough to do SSTO development if done privately as a cut rate Of course they may be over You can also assume that a working SSTO would have other applications that would help pay for its development I'd be inclined to make the prize somewhat larger but might be All work is one man's Henry Spencer U of Toronto Zoology Kipling utzoo henry